Name: DREAM LOGIC
About the game: WHAT IS A LIMINAL SPACE?: Liminal spaces are those strange, evocative, and occasionally unsettling locations that appear to be the entrance to another realm. When someone enters a space that is outside of typical space and time, they are said to be in a condition of liminality. These people straddle the boundaries set by law, custom, and convention for the typical roles, behaviors, and positions. TRUE DREAMLIKE EXPERIENCE: Explore liminal spaces: Pools, School, Hotel, Parking lot, Office and more. Fly through real-time generated clouds. Outrun other vehicles while driving into the sunset. Solve puzzles to advance. CUSTOM ENTITY MODE: Import your own custom entity and try to escape the backrooms. Importing your own entity has never been easier. Import any picture and sound or choose from our presets with just a few clicks. Features in this game mode: Import any picture. Import any sound. Modify volume of imported sound. Modify Player or Entity walk/sprint speed.
